Description:
    Generates pages for the "Pr√©parer mon rendez-vous" section

Example:
    rails generate preparer_page preparer99 --image_name=super.png --department=99

    This will create:
        app/views/pages/preparer99.html.erb

    This will update:
        app/config/routes.rb
        app/controllers/pages_controller.rb
        spec/requests/pages_spec.rb
        config/initializers/themes/default.rb

Notes:

    - Non-reversible. Running 'rails destroy ...' will not revert the updates to the default config file.
    - Need to previously add a picture in the 'app/fronted/images' folder, then use the picture name as an option to the generator.
